<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 10:33:42 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>蓝岭梅尔西果园</title><link>https://some.pics/69db750374297</link><description>&lt;p&gt;位于佐治亚州蓝岭的梅西尔果园是一家备受好评的家族农场，占地300英亩，以其"自摘"苹果体验、烘焙坊和市场而闻名。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A rustic chalkboard lists jam flavors: Christmas, Traffic, Toe, Bear, and Frog, with various fruits like strawberries, blackberries, and tangerines." height="2813" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69db750374297.jpg" width="3751"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 10:33:42 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>蓝岭梅尔西果园</title><link>https://some.pics/69db74d2aa5f9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;位于佐治亚州蓝岭的梅西尔果园是一家备受好评的家族农场，占地300英亩，以其"自摘"苹果体验、烘焙坊和市场而闻名。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A rustic bakery display with stacks of packaged apple cider donuts priced at $9. Warm lighting and wooden decor create a cozy, inviting atmosphere. Signs for other baked goods are visible in the background." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69db74d2aa5f9.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 10:32:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>蓝岭梅尔西果园</title><link>https://some.pics/69db749113632</link><description>&lt;p&gt;位于佐治亚州蓝岭的梅西尔果园是一家备受好评的家族农场，占地300英亩，以其"自摘"苹果体验、烘焙坊和市场而闻名。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A vintage red and white Ford 801 Powermaster tractor is parked indoors. A Mercier Orchards sign hangs in the background, evoking a nostalgic feel." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69db749113632.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 10:31:48 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>夏威夷卡帕阿海滩美景</title><link>https://some.pics/69dac0188507e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;夏威夷卡穆埃拉卡帕阿海滩公园的美丽海岸线照片。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Lovely shoreline pic of Kapa'a Beach Park in Kamuela⁩, Hawaii." height="5291" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/69dac0188507e.jpg" width="3968"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 21:41:47 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>用线串诗，自由创作</title><link>https://some.pics/69dabceacdcb9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我创作了“我们拥抱每一个片段，以解开任何秘密。”；我大概有一天会把它谱成曲…… :)

“这面墙上的文字选自构成此次展览的艺术作品和文字。请选择一种颜色的线，用这些词创作你自己的诗，用多少词随你喜欢。我邀请你造句，或者抛开语法，让联想的跳跃或线的视觉形状来塑造你的语言。”
-克洛伊·马丁内斯，策展人兼驻馆诗人&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An interactive art installation featuring a web of colored strings connected to word tags, with the prompt 'We embrace each partial to unravel any secret.' and an invitation to create a poem using the words displayed." height="2238" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/69dabceacdcb9.jpg" width="1200"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 21:28:14 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>